Summary: a coworker and myself behind a factory and looked up and the stars were blanked out
divs: Sighting DetailsA coworker and myself was behind Federal Mogul a factory in Frankfort Indiana. we looked up noticed the stars were being blanked out no lights in a giant tringler shape moving very slowly we watched it for several minutes until it went away. I thought it was a ufo because of the stars being blanked out in just that area. and then we went back in the plant the thing was traveling from south to north. If there have been any other reports like this around area please let me know about it. Thank You Phil Wessel
trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Frankfort
There were no other sightings in Frankfort on or around June 16th 1981
